---
title: Carb Smart Balsamic-Fig Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Vegetable Medley
description: A medley of veggies and fragrant rosemary are roasted until golden to go alongside this snappy pork tenderloin. The fig and balsamic sauce spooned on top pairs beautifully with all those wonderful flavours!

